0of%20speculation%20about%20how%20many%20more%20cuts%20we%20can%20expect%20this%20year.%20Most%20experts%20are%20split%20between%20one%20additional%20rate%20cut%20or%20two.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBI's%20Jennifer%20Sor%20has%20a%20full%20breakdown%20on%20JPMorgan's%20analysis%20of%20the%20different%20possible%20scenarios%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffed-rate-cut-this-week-fomc-powell-stock-market-outlook-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow%20the%20market%20might%20react%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Sofi's%20head%20of%20investment%20research%20also%20laid%20out%20three%20sectors%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffed-rate-cut-decision-market-impact-stock-picks-sp500-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethat%20could%20come%20away%20the%20biggest%20winners%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt's%20worth%20noting%20that%20even%20%26quot%3Bgood%20news%26quot%3B%20(more%20rate%20cuts%20are%20coming)%20could%20ultimately%20be%20bad%20news%20for%20stocks.%20Remember%3A%20If%20the%20Fed%20gets%20aggressive%20with%20rate%20cuts%2C%20that's%20a%20sign%20it%20believes%20the%20economy%20isn't%20in%20good%20shape%2C%20which%20could%20give%20investors%20pause.%20It%20could%20also%20reignite%20inflation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI'm%20also%20sorry%20to%20say%20there%20won't%20be%20an%20immediate%20impact%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-rate-cut-means-for-americans-credit-cards-savings-mortgages-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efrom%20the%20long-awaited%20rate%20cut%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20most%20of%20us.%20A%20single%2C%20standard%20cut%20won't%20significantly%20drop%20mortgage%20or%20credit-card%20rates%20since%20the%20move%20has%20basically%20been%20priced%20in%20already%2C%20writes%20BI's%20Allie%20Kelly%20and%20Madison%20Hoff.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20so%20much%20riding%20on%20Powell's%20speech%2C%20what%20should%20you%20look%20out%20for%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20spoke%20to%20Aditya%20Bhave%2C%20Bank%20of%20America's%20senior%20US%20Economist%2C%20about%20the%20key%20things%20to%20watch.%20Here's%20what%20he%20flagged%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20dot%20plot%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20first%20thing%20to%20keep%20an%20eye%20on%20is%20the%20Fed's%20updated%20dot%20plot%2C%20which%20is%20a%20chart%20compiling%20Fed%20officials'%20year-end%20projections%20for%20interest%20rates.%20The%20last%20dot%20plot%2C%20which%20was%20published%20in%20June%2C%20had%20a%20median%20projection%20of%20two%20rate%20cuts%20in%202025.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20shift%20of%20the%20median%20dot%20to%20three%20cuts%20in%202025%20would%20signal%20the%20Fed's%20loosening%20up%20its%20policy.%20However%2C%20if%20the%20median%20dot%20remains%20unchanged%2C%20that's%20a%20sign%20the%20central%20bank%20is%20taking%20a%20more%20cautious%20route%2C%20Bhave%20told%20me.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20speech%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIf%20the%20dot%20plot%20disappoints%2C%20fear%20not.%20There's%20always%20Powell's%20speech!%20The%20Fed%20chair%20has%20been%20clear%20his%20focus%20is%20on%20two%20things%3A%20the%20job%20market%20and%20inflation.%20How%20he%20categorizes%20both%20in%20his%20speech%20will%20offer%20up%20some%20big%20clues%20on%20where%20rates%20could%20be%20headed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3ELabor%20market%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3EAny%20discussion%20of%20a%20supply%20slow%20down%20or%20how%20unemployment%20hasn't%20increased%20likely%20means%20Powell's%20taking%20a%20hawkish%2C%20or%20more%20cautious%2C%20approach%20to%20cutting%20rates.%20But%20if%20Powell%20highlights%20demand%20weakness%2C%20the%20increase%20in%20jobless%20claims%2C%20or%20a%20slowdown%20in%20job%20growth%2C%20it's%20game%20on%20for%20more%20cuts.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EInflation%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3EIf%20Powell%20mentions%20the%20%26quot%3Bstickiness%26quot%3B%20of%20inflation%20and%20dismisses%20the%20impact%20of%20tariffs%2C%20Bhave%20said%20that%20could%20spell%20trouble%20for%20people%20hoping%20for%20more%20cuts.%20However%2C%20if%20he%20points%20to%20inflation%20being%20impacted%20by%20the%20one-off%20nature%20of%20tariffs%2C%20today's%20cut%20could%20be%20the%20start%20of%20something%20bigger.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjerome-powell-fed-interest-rate-cut-stock-market-expectation-2025-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1758104097000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a78e64194a2d49b8aef8be%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjerome-powell-fed-interest-rate-cut-stock-market-expectation-2025-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20rate%20cut%20is%20coming.%20But%20what%20comes%20after%20that%2C%20and%20how%20the%20market%20reacts%2C%20isn't%20as%20clear.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ddefrancesco%40businessinsider.com%20(Dan%20DeFrancesco)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjerome-powell-fed-interest-rate-cut-stock-market-expectation-2025-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Not%20a%20fan'%3A%20Dana%20White%20makes%20blunt%20confession%20about%20WWE%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1758103955000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-123941946%2Cimgsize-627277.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Finternational-sports%2Fdana-white-makes-blunt-confession-about-wwe-and-explains-why-he-does-not-watch-it%2Farticleshow%2F123941992.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22UFC%20President%20Dana%20White%20reiterate