essinsider.com%2Fsmall-cap-stock-picks-bank-of-america-ark-bbwi-gtlb-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehas%20shifted%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20positive%20direction.%20Thomas%20thinks%20a%20rate%20cut%20means%20their%20performance%20is%20more%20likely%20to%20let%20them%20catch%20up%20to%20large-cap%20peers%20in%20the%20final%20stretch%20of%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20investors%20seem%20to%20be%20talking%20about%20the%20opportunity%20for%20small-caps%20to%20not%20only%20catch%20up%20but%20find%20durable%20outperformance%20during%20this%20cutting%20cycle%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20area%20of%20the%20market%20Thomas%20sees%20benefiting%20from%20a%20cut%20is%20%3Cstrong%3Efinancials%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20The%20sector%20has%20rallied%20recently%2C%20but%20could%20have%20even%20more%20gas%20in%20the%20tank%20after%20a%20cut.%20Financials%20are%20also%20sensitive%20to%20interest%20rates%2C%20and%20while%20lower%20rates%20mean%20lower%20interest%20income%20for%20banks%2C%20it%20could%20also%20mean%20more%20lending%20activity%20broadly%20as%20businesses%20and%20consumers%20refinance%20or%20take%20out%20new%20debt%20at%20more%20attractive%20rates.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20a%20big%20part%20of%20some%20of%20that%20is%20also%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20Treasury%20market%20has%20not%20gotten%20out%20of%20hand%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20touting%20the%20recent%20gains%20in%20both%20financials%20and%20small-cap%20stocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20Thomas%20said%20she%20sees%20potential%20momentum%20ahead%20for%20the%20%3Cstrong%3Ereal%20estate%20market%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20%26quot%3BYou%20probably%20see%20the%20housing%20market%20start%20to%20feel%20a%20little%20bit%20better%20about%20itself%2C%20because%20mortgage%20rates%20are%20likely%20to%20come%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20she%20acknowledged%20that%20mortgages%20aren't%20likely%20to%20fall%20by%20too%20much%20if%20the%2010-year%20Treasury%20y