metimes%20force%20her%20to%20come%20on%20the%20evening%20walk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20and%20family%20are%20non-negotiable%2C%20and%20my%20nights%20are%20about%20them.%20My%20husband%20cooks%20%E2%80%94%20I%20haven't%20cooked%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20and%20the%20last%20time%20I%20tried%20to%2C%20we%20ended%20up%20ordering%20pizza.%20I'm%20thankful%20that%20I%20don't%20have%20to%20think%20about%20what%20to%20make%20for%20dinner%2C%20and%20he's%20an%20amazing%20chef.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20go-to%20is%20homemade%20gnocchi%20with%20a%20creamy%20pesto.%20We'll%20share%20details%20of%20our%20days%20as%20he%20cooks%2C%20though%20it's%20usually%20me%20talking%20at%20him%20more%20than%20the%20other%20way%20around.%20It's%20also%20rare%20that%20I%20don't%20connect%20with%20my%20best%20friends%20each%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20a%20huge%20believer%20in%20being%20an%20accessible%20leader%2C%20so%20I%20respond%20to%20messages%20as%20they%20come%20in%2C%20even%20if%20it's%20pretty%20late.%20When%20we%20sit%20down%20to%20dinner%2C%20though%2C%20I%20try%20to%20put%20my%20phone%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2257dffd81-eaa3-48c9-88aa-bfd65dfa725f%5C%22%3EAfter%20dinner%2C%20we%20unwind%20with%20a%20book%20or%20TV%20show%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20it's%20basketball%20season%2C%20I%20watch%20my%20beloved%20Celtics.%20I%20love%20a%20romance%20novel%2C%20and%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20recently%20started%20re-watching%20%26quot%3BCrash%20Landing%20on%20You%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Korean%20romantic%20comedy%20and%20drama.%20It's%20the%20best%20show%20on%20Netflix.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Emily%20Fontaine%20meeting%20with%20her%20team%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68c82287f9db348adc0b77a0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222433%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFontaine%20often%20meets%20with%20members%20of%20her%20team.%3Cp%3EEmily%20Fontaine%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI