ek%20marked%20the%20busiest%20period%20for%20IPOs%20since%202021%2C%20and%20ticket%20reseller%20StubHub%2C%20which%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fipo-comeback-victim-trump-tariffs-stock-market-crash-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edelayed%20its%20IPO%20after%20the%20market%20plunged%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20April%2C%20is%20set%20to%20begin%20trading%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20order%20books%20are%20as%20large%20as%20we've%20seen%2C%20and%20we're%20seeing%20participation%20across%20all%20global%20investor%20types%2C%26quot%3B%20Sumit%20Mukherjee%2C%20head%20of%20market%20intelligence%20for%20equity%20capital%20markets%20at%20JP%20Morgan%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BRecent%20interest%20is%20even%20in%20excess%20of%20what%20we%20experienced%20during%20the%202021%20wave%2C%20when%20the%20enthusiasm%20for%20IPOs%20was%20strong.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmong%20last%20week's%20top%20six%20listings%2C%20which%20raised%20more%20than%20%244%20billion%20between%20them%2C%20was%20%26quot%3Bbuy%20now%2C%20pay%20later%26quot%3B%20giant%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fklarna-ipo-stock-price-investors-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKlarna.%3C%2Fa%3E%20The%20%26quot%3Bbuy%20now%2C%20pay%20later%26quot%3B%20giant%20raised%20%241.37%20billion%20in%20its%20IPO%20after%20delaying%20the%20listing%20earlier%20this%20year.%20The%20next%20day%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthis-venture-firm-is-the-biggest-winner-in-figures-ipo-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eblockchain%20lender%20Figure%20went%20public%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20raising%20nearly%20%24800%20million%20in%20its%20IPO.%20Its%20shares%20are%20now%20trading%20over%2060%25%20above%20their%20IPO%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMukherjee%20said%20he%20expects%20at%20least%2015%20IPOs%20to%20launch%20this%20month.%20Between%20October%20and%20December%2C%20he%20said%20the%20public%20markets%20could%20%26quot%3Beasily%26quot%3B%20see%2020%20to%2025%20more%20listings%20amid%20roaring%20investor%20demand%20for%20more%20IPOs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20may%20be%20more%20buyers%20clamoring%20for%20new%20listings%20than%20there%20are%20top%20companies%20ready%20to%20list%2C%20Mukherjee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20expects%20more%20companies%20to%20begin%20preparing%20to%20go%20public%20this%20year%20and%20in%202026%20as%20new%20listings%20%26quot%3Brebuild%20confidence%20in%20the%20IPO%20market.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20so%20much%20capital%20available%20in%20the%20private%20markets%20and%20copious%20regulations%20placed%20on%20public%20companies%2C%20however%2C%20some%20investors%20aren't%20sure%20this%20year's%20listings%20will%20provide%20enough%20motivation%20to%20new%20IPO%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20bankers%20assume%20that%20companies%20want%20to%20go%20public%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20think%20there's%20the%20same%20desire%20that%20there%20used%20to%20be%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Peter%20H%C3%A9bert%2C%20partner%20and%20cofounder%20of%20VC%20firm%20Lux%20Capital.%20%26quot%3BFor%20the%20largest%2C%20most%20advantaged%20companies%20right%20now%2C%20I%20can't%20think%20of%20much%20of%20a%20reason%20to%20go%20public.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20tension%20appears%20to%20be%20catching%20the%20White%20House's%20attention%2C%20too.%20In%20a%20Truth%20Social%20post%20Monday%2C%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20suggested%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-wants-company-earnings-change-6-months-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecompanies%20should%20only%20be%20required%20to%20report%20their%20earnings%20every%20six%20months%3C%2Fa%3E%20rather%20than%20quarterly.%20Such%20a%20change%2C%20which%20would%20be%20subject%20to%20SEC%20approval%2C%20could%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-quarterly-reporting-plan-corporate-earnings-investors-retail-traders-investing-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bsave%20money%20and%20allow%20managers%20to%20focus%20on%20properly%20running%20their%20companies%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20Trump%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b7ca95ff-d093-4660-9723-c7f40ddfcdb6%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EReframing%20the%20IPO%20pop%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20three-year%20IPO%20drought%2C%20pent-up%20public%20market%20demand%20has%20helped%20fuel%20major%20IPO%20pops%20this%20year.%20Design%20software%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwho-got-rich-on-figma-ipo-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFigma's%20stock%3C%2Fa%3E%20jumped%20more%20than%20300%25%20over%20its%20IPO%20price%20in%20the%20first%20week%20after%20its%20July%20IPO%2C%20while%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcircle-stock-price-usd-coin-crypto-crcl-ipo-genius-act-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecrypto%20company%20Circle%3C%2Fa%3E%20surged%20more%20than%20800%25%20over%20its%20IPO%20price%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20blockbuster%20IPOs%20have%20helped%20drum%20up%20further%20investor%20enthusiasm.%20But%20for%20startup%20founders%20and%20investors%2C%20they've%20come%20at%20the%20literal%20expense%20of%20significant%20discounts%20to%20company%20shares.%20Nearly%20every%20major%20public%20listing%20in%20the%20second%20quarter%20of%20the%20year%20was%20priced%20below%20the%20companies'%20peak%20private%20valuations%2C%20according%20to%20PitchBook%3B%20Circle%2C%20for%20example%2C%20was%20last%20privately%20valued%20at%20%249%20billion%20in%202022%20but%20valued%20at%20%246.9%20billion%20in%20its%20IPO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20discounts%20have%20indeed%20helped%20fuel%20IPO%20demand%2C%20said%20Jimmy%20Williams%2C%20head%20of%20West%20Coast%20equity%20capital%20markets%20for%20the%20bank's%20tech%2C%20media%2C%20and%20telecommunications%20segment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20broader%20market%20is%20really%20expensive%2C%20investors%20can%20look%20to%20IPOs%20for%20alpha%2C%20because%20they're%20priced%20at%20a%20discount%20to%20fair%20value%20to%20incentivize%20investors%20to%20buy%20the%20stock%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAs%20a%20result%2C%20they%20generally%20trade%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20companies%20going%20public%20this%20fall%20aren't%20seeing%20the%20same%20degree%20of%20IPO%20pops%20from%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECrypto%20exchange%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgemini-ipo-stock-price-rally-winklevoss-twins-crypto-tech-klarna-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGemini%20Space%20Station%3C%2Fa%3E%20recorded%20the%20highest%20IPO%20pop%20of%20September%20so%20far%20after%20its%20shares%20surged%20over%2060%25%20above%20its%20IPO%20price%20on%20the%20stock's%20first%20day%20of%20trading%2C%20in%20part%20due%20to%20the%20company%20allocating%20an%20outsize%20portion%20of%20its%20IPO%20to%20retail%20traders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20that's%20just%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20250%25%20pop%20Figma%20saw%20on%20its%20first%20day%20of%20trading%2C%20and%20Gemini's%20shares%20have%20fallen%20in%20the%20days%20since%20to%20settle%20closer%20to%2015%25%20above%20their%20IPO%20price.%20Other%20pops%20this%20month%20have%20been%20more%20modest%2C%20like%20Klarna's%2C%20which%20saw%20the%20fintech%20company's%20stock%20open%2030%25%20over%20its%20IPO%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hoopla%20in%20front%20of%20the%20New%20York%20Stock%20Exchange%20decorated%20for%20the%20initial%20public%20offering%20of%20the%20collaborative%20design%20application%20Figma%2C%20on%20Thursday%2C%20July%2031%2C%202025.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F688bd3093d5881a51c1e6541%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHoopla%20in%20front%20of%20the%20New%20York%20Stock%20Exchange%20decorated%20for%20the%20initial%20public%20offering%20of%20the%20collaborative%20design%20application%20Figma%2C%20on%20Thursday%2C%20July%2031%2C%202025.%3Cp%3ERichard%20B.%20Levine%2FSipa%20USA%20via%20Reuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBankers%20attributed%20the%20diminishing%20pop%20to%20a%20few%20factors.%20For%20one%2C%20as%20more%20companies%20go%20public%2C%20banks%20can%20more%20easily%20price%20some%20subsequent%20candidates%20by%20comparing%20them%20to%20their%20peers%20in%20the%20same%20sector.%20And%2C%20because%20investor%20demand%20for%20IPOs%20is%20outpacing%20supply%2C%20many%20IPO%20candidates%20now%20have%20more%20power%20to%20push%20for%20better%20pricing%2C%20said%20Gregor%20Feige%2C%20head%20of%20UBS'%20Americas%20equity%20capital%20markets%20unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20competitive%20pricing%20and%20decreased%20likelihood%20of%20IPO%20volatility%20could%20be%20a%20boon%20for%20the%20next%20wave%20of%20companies%20considering%20public%20market%20debuts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20if%20we%20had%20a%20bunch%20of%20Figma-like%20IPOs%20with%20big%20price%20fluctuations%20in%20the%20fall%2C%20people%20would%20say%2C%20what's%20going%20on%20with%20the%20market%3F%20Why%20are%20these%20IPOs%20getting%20so%20mispriced%20vis-%C3%A0-vis%20demand%3F%26quot%3B%20Williams%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20healthy%20that%20we're%20seeing%20discounts%20tighten%20and%20aftermarket%20performance%20moderate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20crypto%20has%20reigned%20supreme%20in%20the%20IPO%20market%20this%20year%2C%20bringing%20companies%20to%20market%20like%20Circle%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbullish-ipo-blsh-stock-price-crypto-peter-thiel-nyse-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBullish%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Gemini%2C%20Mukherjee%20expects%20the%20fall%20IPO%20push%20to%20help%20widen%20the%20aperture%20for%20more%20IPOs%20next%20year%20across%20more%20varied%20sectors%20and%20growth%20profiles.%20Black%20Rock%20Coffee%20Ba