to%20want%20to%20see%20liquidity%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20there%20needs%20to%20be%20some%20point%20at%20which%20most%20of%20these%20companies%20go%20public.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELiquidity%20has%20remained%20a%20concern%20for%20many%20investors%20as%20companies%20stay%20private%20for%20longer%2C%20even%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsecondary-deal-etiquette-keeping-vcs-from-getting-liquidity-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esecondary%20markets%20surge%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Feige%20added%20that%20more%20companies%20are%20including%20secondary%20transactions%20in%20their%20IPOs%2C%20which%20can%20help%20provide%20additional%20immediate%20liquidity%20to%20early%20employees%20and%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20top%20IPOs%20like%20Figma%20certainly%20grab%20investor%20attention%2C%20a%20few%20standout%20listings%20won't%20be%20enough%20to%20grant%20the%20IPO%20market%20a%20full%20rebound%2C%20Zheng%20said.%20Instead%2C%20whether%20the%20IPO%20window%20reopens%20across%20all%20sectors%20will%20depend%20on%20the%20sustained%20pace%20of%20VC-backed%20companies%20coming%20to%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHaving%20a%20consistent%20cadence%20of%20companies%20that%20go%20public%2C%20get%20good%20public%20investor%20demand%2C%20and%20continue%20to%20do%20well%2C%20will%20bolster%20confidence%20across%20more%20startups%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbankers-say-ipo-demand-back-to-2021-levels-supply-2025-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1758099601000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68c8c0b8183847aa39d6d1c2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbankers-say-ipo-demand-back-to-2021-levels-supply-2025-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Public%20investors%20are%20clamoring%20for%20new%20IPOs.%20But%20some%20bankers%20