by%20flooding%20the%20pipes.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine's%20war%20is%20starting%20to%20go%20below%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussian%20troops%20were%20recently%20found%20attempting%20to%20infiltrate%20battle%20lines%20in%20Kharkiv%20by%20crawling%20through%20an%20underground%20pipe%2C%20with%20Kyiv's%20forces%20trying%20to%20stop%20them%20by%20flooding%20or%20fortifying%20such%20ducts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20observers%20publicly%20identified%20the%20pipeline%20tactic%20last%20week%20in%20Kupiansk%2C%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-retreats-from-kharkiv-region-after-ukrainian-forces-advanced-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecity%20in%20the%20Kharkiv%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0region%20that%20has%20seen%20heavy%20fighting%20along%20the%20front%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20the%20third%20time%20since%20the%20war%20began%20that%20Russian%20forces%20have%20been%20found%20crawling%20or%20walking%20in%20gas%20or%20water%20pipes%20to%20avoid%20detection%2C%20and%20the%20tactic%20could%20present%20a%20growing%20defensive%20challenge%20for%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDeepState%2C%20an%20oft-cited%20Ukrainian%20open-source%20intelligence%20group%2C%20reported%20on%20Friday%20that%20Russian%20troops%20had%20used%20a%20gas%20pipe%20near%20Kupiansk%20to%20sneak%20past%20the%20nearby%20Oskil%20River%20and%20establish%20supply%20lines%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcombat-drone-pilot-trainer-russia-ukraine-war-music-background-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edrone%20pilot%20positions%3C%2Fa%3E%20closer%20to%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20group's%20analysts%20published%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FDeepStateUA%2F22459%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edrone%20footage%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20a%20uniformed%20soldier%20dragging%20a%20package%20out%20of%20a%20hole%20in%20a%20forested%20area.%20The%20report%20was%20echoed%20on%20Russian%20social%20media%20channels%2C%20acc