wing%20the%20duct%20to%20flood.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20does%20not%20mean%20that%20over%20time%20the%20enemy%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20restore%20this%20pipe%2C%20but%20it%20is%20being%20monitored%20closely%2C%26quot%3B%20Fedorenko%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20Ukrainian%20military%20bloggers%20said%20on%20Sunday%20that%20Kyiv's%20forces%20laid%20barbed%20wire%20inside%20at%20least%20one%20pipeline%2C%20circulating%20a%20video%20that%20appears%20to%20show%20the%20pipe's%20booby-trapped%20interior.%20The%20clip%20has%20not%20been%20confirmed%20by%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tactic%20of%20using%20underground%20pipes%20mirrors%20a%20bold%20Russian%20operation%20in%20March%20that%20saw%20the%20Kremlin's%20special%20forces%20walking%20roughly%20nine%20miles%20through%20a%20gas%20pipe%20in%20Sudzha%20to%20strike%20at%20the%20Ukrainian%20rear%20in%20Kursk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20officials%20said%20the%20pipe%20was%20unused%20and%20had%20a%20diameter%20of%201.4%20meters%2C%20or%20about%20four%20and%20a%20half%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Russia%20hailed%20the%20attack%20as%20a%20success%2C%20Ukraine%20said%20it%20later%20discovered%20the%20saboteur%20team%20and%20killed%20most%20of%20them.%20Most%20of%20Ukraine's%20forces%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-losing-sudzha-final-stronghold-bargaining-chip-kursk-russia-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eretreated%20from%20Kursk%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20early%202024%2C%20Russian%20troops%20were%20reported%20by%20Ukrainian%20media%20to%20have%20drained%20a%20service%20water%20pipe%20in%20Avdiivka%2C%20Donetsk%2C%20using%20it%20to%20advance%20underground%20and%20installing%20exit%20holes%20every%20300%20feet%20or%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-lost-weirdest-wartime-income-streams-gas-pipeline-ukraine-deal-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMajor%20gas%20pipelines%3C%2