uyers%20each%20year%20used%20a%20gift%20or%20loan%20from%20family%20and%20friends%2C%20data%20from%20the%20National%20Association%20of%20Realtors%20shows.%20For%20buyers%20of%20all%20types%2C%20family%20swooped%20in%20to%20help%20about%2016%25%20of%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConditions%20would%20appear%20ripe%20for%20nepo%20buyers'%20numbers%20to%20spike%20%E2%80%94%20with%20prices%20high%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhomebuyers-mortgage-rate-buydown-points-real-estate-prices-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eborrowing%20rates%20still%20steep%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20lots%20of%20home%20shoppers%20could%20use%20a%20hand.%20Many%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbaby-boomers-real-estate-millennials-inheriting-home-taxes-trust-retirement-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebaby%20boomers%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20sitting%20on%20piles%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhome-equity-investments-heloc-refinance-loan-investors-homeownership-housing-market-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehome%20equity%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20bulging%20investment%20portfolios%20that%20they%20could%20theoretically%20tap%20to%20aid%20their%20millennial%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-how-i-bought-home-new-york-city-apartment-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGen%20Z%20offspring%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Yet%20the%20nepo%20homebuyer%20is%20actually%20in%20decline.%20The%20past%20few%20years%20of%20NAR%20data%20have%20shown%20a%20significant%20dip%20from%20the%20historical%20average%3A%20In%202024%2C%20only%20a%20quarter%20of%20first-time%20buyers%20got%20help%20from%20friends%20and%20family.%20For%20all%20buyers%2C%20this%20share%20has%20slipped%20to%20just%2010%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20downturn%20defies%20conventional%20thinking.%20The%20market%20has%20been%20so%20brutal%20for%20young%20buyers%20that%20it%20can%20be%20hard%20to%20imagine%20someone%20making%20it%20