from%20the%20forest%20next%20door.%20They%20observed%20the%20forest%20and%20the%20species%20that%20grew%20there%20and%20worked%20on%20recreating%20the%20broken%20linkages%20between%20different%20species%20and%20creating%20an%20interdependence%20between%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FInfographic-website-33-1724828441.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22how%20to%20build%20a%20biosphere%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FInfographic-website-33-1724828441.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FInfographic-website-33-1724828441-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FInfographic-website-33-1724828441-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FInfographic-website-33-1724828441-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FInfographic-website-33-1724828441-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-363141%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20the%20Rajaji%20Raghati%20Biosphere%20is%20rich%20in%20biodiversity%20and%20home%20to%20132%20native%20plant%20species%2C%20including%20many%20that%20had%20all%20but%20disappeared%20from%20the%20region.%20Their%20efforts%20have%20also%20attracted%20a%20diverse%20array%20of%20wildlife%20%E2%80%94%20from%20leopards%20and%20elephants%20to%20an%20abundance%20of%20bird%20species%20%E2%80%94%20all%20of%20which%20are%20now%20regular%20visitors%20to%20the%20biosphere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20saplings%20are%20now%20about%20six%20feet%20high%2C%20and%20when%20you%20walk%2C%20you%20feel%20like%20you%E2%80%99re%20walking%20on